In view of the foregoing, we have recommended that Management:

•	Maximize the utilization of the 20% Development Fund, and that proper planning should be made, so that all its programmed development projects during the year could be implemented immediately for the benefit of its constituents;

•	Require the City Development Council to identify and prepare a detailed list of priority projects to be funded under the 20% Development Fund including time lines so that proper monitoring can be undertaken and that all its programmed development projects during the year could be implemented immediately.
